    "body": "Because it's runtime behaviour so on the Limited API it needs to be decided with the runtime version.\r\n\r\nThe change of declaration from `int` to `enum` is to avoid the problem with trying to overwrite names when using `from something import *`. I think that may be fixed anyway, but `enum` definitely avoids it.",
    "closed_at": null,
